1) App behavior

The main web app exposes test buttons for:

External fast URL
External slow URL
External missing URL
Same-namespace microservice
Other-namespace microservice
Blocked microservice protected by a NetworkPolicy

Suggested endpoints:

EXTERNAL_FAST_URL=https://www.redhat.com
EXTERNAL_SLOW_URL=https://httpbin.org/delay/5
EXTERNAL_MISSING_URL=https://does-not-exist.invalid

The .invalid domain is useful for a guaranteed failure path in demos.
